'''Dr. Bones''' is a skeleton.

==History==
Bones is a full-size skeleton decoration at [[Emerald City Bar|Joe's bar]]. He is adorned with white Christmas lights and a sign that says "Dr. Bones on call!" He is displayed because the bar is said to be across from the hospital, so it is a local hangout for the doctors and staff that work there.
